@baseUrl = https://web-production-cf40e.up.railway.app

### Verificar una foto (POST /verify)
POST {{baseUrl}}/verify
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary123

------boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample.jpg
------boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="lat"

-34.6037
------boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="lon"

-58.3816
------boundary123--

### Consultar una verificacion (GET /verify/<id>)
# Pegar aca el verification_id que devolvio el request de arriba
GET {{baseUrl}}/verify/38f35dd6-53d6-4e43-b48b-1ec151c8d22b
